column1: # "aotearoa_mini" remix - the "aotearoa" remix without biomes, decorations or ores (or the base
#       package; there are no ABM/LBM packages to omit)
# unilib provides a set of custom dirt-with-turf nodes, to replace the widespread (and
#   unimaginative) use of dirts from minetest_game. The custom nodes are disabled by default;
#   enable them by uncommenting the optional package below
# Optional package. Uncomment this package to replace minetest_game dirt-with-turf nodes with
